These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, mystery, scientific
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, subway, taxi
1. the person watching adventure movies is the person driving the subway##1
2. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
4. the person driving the subway is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | scientific | mystery    |
| Transport     | subway    | taxi       | snowmobile |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, librarian, pilot
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, handball, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
2. the pilot is on the left of the fisherman##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left or far right##3
4. the librarian is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Job     | pilot | fisherman | librarian  |
| Sport   | golf  | handball  | ice-hockey |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, paramedic, videographer
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, r&b, techno
1. the fan of r&b is on the far left or far right##3
2. the accountant is on the far right##1
3. the paramedic is the fan of techno##1
4. the fan of r&b is on the right of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Job           | videographer | paramedic | accountant |
| Music-Genre   | blues        | techno    | r&b        |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, fishing, video-games
3 different pets are kept: fish, guinea-pig, mouse
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
3. the owner of the fish is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the owner of the mouse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | video-games | fishing | baking |
| Pet     | guinea-pig  | fish    | mouse  |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, disaster, family
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, subway, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
2. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
4. the person watching action movies is between the person watching disaster movies and the person driving the taxi##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | action | family |
| Transport     | subway   | ship   | taxi   |

