.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, rock, techno
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, dutch, malaysian
1. the fan of techno is on the right of the dutch##1
2. the malaysian is on the left of the fan of funk##1
3. the malaysian is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | rock  | techno    | funk       |
| Nationality   | dutch | malaysian | australian |

