.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, milk
There 3 different types of food: grapes, orange, pomegranate
1. the person drinking cola is the person eating grapes##1
2. the person eating orange is in the middle##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |   3    |
| Beverage   | milk        | fanta  | cola   |
| Food       | pomegranate | orange | grapes |

