.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-12::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, tea, water
There are 3 different nationalities: american, german, russian
1. the american is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking tea##2
2. the german is the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking water##1
4. the american is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3    |
| Beverage      | tea    | water    | sprite  |
| Nationality   | german | american | russian |

