The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, martial-arts, superhero
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | sprite    | hot-chocolate | 7up         |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | martial-arts  | documentary |

